{"tid":2213361,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"150根本係無差別十三億人，唔係廢坑蝗妻愛情故事","createTime":"2020-09-22T12:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T05:57:32.000Z","uid":301952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9840b92df694542c0ed658ada154c95813dd71","tid":2213361,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:49:56.000Z","msg":"關愛基金將向低收入家庭新來港定居人士發放一次過1萬元津貼，合資格申請人今日起可於各中銀香港分行及各區民政諮詢中心等索取表格， 星期日起接受申請。今早9時許，在深水埗一間中國銀行有數名市民索取表格。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"green\">現年67歲的蘇先生來港約4年</span></strong></span>，本身任職清潔工，自今年4月起失業，現時領取綜援，因此前來取申請表。<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"green\">家庭主婦曹太太與丈夫來港均未足7年</span></strong></span>，她說任職保安的丈夫，月入僅1萬多元，相信兩人都符合資格申領。不過，她說申請表的字體細小，擔心未必懂得填寫，又說最快要等8星期才可領取津貼是有點遲，希望越早越好。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550941-20200922.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550941-20200922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=397d068e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550941-20200922.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f963bcd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550941-20200922.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">67歲 (-4) = 63歲都黎到，我唔撚信係港女嫁你！<br />\n曹生曹太又憑咩黎申請居港權 ??<br />\n根本百五部隊好多唔關廢坑蝗妻，直頭係十三億人無差別殖民</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcb968fcbb79efa36c4d9207b1a8df989135fd7","tid":2213361,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:54:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f56d65ff70f6c03382552f58ee3bf9dbadea624","tid":2213361,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T12:59:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ac385aff736fa9ca6160d026b1c6d62a460cd9","tid":2213361,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86116181e7961a596c3d1b8278a54b31c8882947","tid":2213361,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"真心想知嗰位『曹太與丈夫』係經咩途徑嚟到香港？"},{"pid":"5732f229cdd72679ef439132090f092aa7094559","tid":2213361,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86116181e7961a596c3d1b8278a54b31c8882947","tid":2213361,"uid":64603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"真心想知嗰位『曹太與丈夫』係經咩途徑嚟到香港？"